# Monorepo ignore rules

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/

# Build outputs
**/.next/
**/out/
**/dist/
**/build/

# Coverage
**/coverage/

# Environment files
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.pnpm-debug.log*

# OS / Editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# TypeScript
**/*.tsbuildinfo
